### âž¤ Basics: Using `System.IO.File`

| Operation       | Method                            |
|----------------|------------------------------------|
| Read All Text  | `File.ReadAllText(path)`           |
| Write All Text | `File.WriteAllText(path, content)` |
| Append Text    | `File.AppendAllText(path, text)`   |

> âœ… These methods are **synchronous**. Use `File.ReadAllTextAsync` etc. for **async I/O**.

